text: Johannes Nilsson (born March 16, 1995) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Brynäs IF of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Nilsson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Brynäs IF during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Brynäs IF players Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards
